title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 24 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 24 2022
description:
The Biden administration is running out of excuses. Biden says high gas prices are good for you, Harris says the baby formula crisis is under control. When even Stephen Colbert makes a joke about how bad things are, you know Dems are in trouble. GA primary day with C&B: Football great and Senate candidate Herschel Walker joins Clay and Buck to make his case to the voters. Biden's stupid covid spending caused inflation.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
